OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,FThames Water has been fined #122.7
OL,8,Fmillion after two investigations into
OL,9,Fwastewater and dividend payments, in
OL,10,Fthe largest penalty Ofwat has ever
OL,11,Fissued, the regulator said.
OL,13,FThe water giant will pay #104.5
OL,14,Fmillion for breaches of rules relating
OL,15,Fto its wastewater operations, after
OL,16,FOfwat said it "failed to protect the
OL,17,Fenvironment".
