OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,FOfwat chief executive David Black
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our investigation has uncovered
OL,9,Fa series of failures by the company to
OL,10,Fbuild, maintain and operate adequate
OL,11,Finfrastructure to meet its obligations.
OL,13,F"The company also failed to come up
OL,14,Fwith an acceptable redress package
OL,15,Fthat would have benefited the
OL,16,Fenvironment, so we have imposed a
OL,17,Fsignificant financial penalty."
