OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,FThames Water will pay an extra #18.2
OL,8,Fmillion for breaking rules related to
OL,9,Fdividend payments, the first ever
OL,10,Fdividend-related fine, Ofwat said.
OL,12,FThe regulator said the money will be
OL,13,Fpaid by the utility giant and its
OL,14,Finvestors, not by customers.
OL,16,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said:
OL,17,F"The era of profiting from failure is
OL,18,Fover. The Government is cleaning up
OL,19,Four rivers, lakes and seas for good."
