OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,FThe wastewater fine was first proposed
OL,8,Flast year and confirmed on Wednesday.
OL,10,FA Thames Water spokesperson said: "We
OL,11,Ftake our responsibility towards the
OL,12,Fenvironment very seriously and note
OL,13,Fthat Ofwat acknowledges we have
OL,14,Falready made progress to address
OL,15,Fissues raised in the investigation
OL,16,Frelating to storm overflows.
OL,18,F"The dividends were declared following
OL,19,Fa consideration of the company's legal
OL,20,Fand regulatory obligations.
